title: Georges Seurat A Sunday on La Grande Jatte—1884 Umbrella
description:
Umbrella developed from Georges Seurat’s A Sunday on La Grande Jatte—1884, 1884-86, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection

Open up a masterpiece and take it with you a rainy day to keep you dry, or protect you from the sun.

  • Dimensions: Closed- 9.5 x 2 in. Open- 38 in.
  • Materials: Polyester, Plastic, Aluminum.
  • Auto open, close.
  • Come with protective sleeve.
